  following her divorce from kelly , blair moved permanently to europe where she paired off with french actor and director roger pigaut , and continued to appear in films , including juan antonio bardem 's calle mayor ( 1956 ) and michelangelo antonioni 's il grido ( 1957 ) .

heavens to betsy ! : betsy blair was nominated for a 1955 oscar for playing ernest borgnine 's shy girlfriend in this film

